<ul>
<li><strong>Collaboration with regulators: </strong>Ripple actively engages with regulators worldwide, including the SEC, to stay updated on regulatory requirements and ensure compliance.</li>



<li><strong>Adherence to AML and KYC regulations:</strong> Ripple follows strict anti-money laundering (AML) and know your customer (KYC) regulations to prevent illegal activities and maintain transparency.</li>



<li><strong>Transparency and visibility:</strong> Ripple provides real-time visibility into transactions and ensures traceability, helping regulators monitor and enforce compliance in the cryptocurrency space.</li>
</ul>



